&lt;p&gt;&lt;img data-src=&#34;https://quasdo.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20221018152011730.png&#34; alt=&#34;image-20221018152011730&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;struct —— 访问控制默认 public&lt;/p&gt;
